<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>🦞 康复日历</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="dashboard-container compact-dashboard">
        <header class="hero compact-hero">
            <div class="hero-text">
                <h1>康复日历</h1>
                <p class="subtitle">右侧链重排 · 脚踝控制 · 肩颈减压</p>
            </div>
        </header>

        <section class="card observation-card compact-card">
            <div id="dailyTitle" class="daily-title">
                <div class="title-main">📈 今日观察</div>
                <div class="title-subtitle"></div>
            </div>
            <div id="dailyObservation" class="daily-observation">
                <div class="observation-content">今日无</div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="card chart-section compact-card">
            <div class="section-title-row compact-title-row">
                <div class="title-with-date">
                    <h2>📈 康复轨迹</h2>
                    <span class="current-date" id="currentDate"></span>
                </div>
                <div class="range-tabs" aria-label="图表范围切换">
                    <button type="button" class="range-tab active" data-range="7">7天</button>
                    <button type="button" class="range-tab" data-range="30">30天</button>
                    <button type="button" class="range-tab" data-range="90">90天</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="chart-container chart-compact">
                <canvas id="progressChart"></canvas>
            </div>
            <div class="chart-inline-legend" aria-label="趋势线标注">
                <div class="chart-inline-legend-item">
                    <span class="chart-inline-line chart-inline-line-green"></span>
                    <span>整体体感</span>
                </div>
                <div class="chart-inline-legend-item">
                    <span class="chart-inline-line chart-inline-line-red"></span>
                    <span>完成度</span>
                </div>
                <div class="chart-inline-legend-item">
                    <span class="chart-inline-line chart-inline-line-blue"></span>
                    <span>日常注意度</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <div class="compact-layout tighter-layout">
            <section class="card analysis-section unified-card compact-card">
                <h2>🧠 问题解析</h2>
                <div class="body-diagram-container">
                    <img src="body-diagram.jpg" alt="姿态问题示意图" class="body-diagram-img">
                </div>
                <div class="summary-box analysis-box compact-summary-box">
                    <p><strong>起点：</strong>右脚踝旧伤 + 久坐 + 颈椎旧问题，三者共同作用。</p>
                    <p><strong>核心问题：</strong>右侧下腰—胯—胸整条链容易留在后面，形成左前 / 右后的三维不对称。身体为了维持平衡，左腰代偿性紧张，右肩前卷，颈椎受累。<br><em>2026-04-06 补充：</em>右脚外侧韧带旧伤还导致<strong>抬脚困难</strong>，使得身体更依赖前脚掌直接找支撑，而不是顺畅走完脚跟→中足→前足的受力路径。</p>
                    <p><strong>为什么不是单纯练肌肉：</strong>问题不在某块肌肉弱，而在整条姿态链的位置错了。如果只练力量，右侧还是会习惯性缩在后面。</p>
                    <p><strong>康复原则：</strong>先重排右侧姿态链（让右下腰、右胯、右胸回到前方支撑位），再用少量有效动作找控制、找连接、找稳定。不走纯增肌路线。</p>
                    <p><strong>当前核心指标：</strong>整体体感（今天身体顺不顺）、完成度（训练有没有做）、成果守住度（白天有没有把成果又耗回去）。</p>
                    <p><strong>当前主线动作：</strong>死虫式、Bird Dog、W字开肩、胸椎右旋、坐姿骨盆中立、单脚站立、右脚后跟找地、右后开弓动作。</p>
                    <p><strong>日常提示词：</strong>右脚接地 / 右胯前接 / 右胸打开 / 肩后下、脖子放松。<strong>右脚前脚掌别偷偷抢支撑，中足和后跟也要参与。</strong></p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="card today-section compact-card">
                <div class="section-title-row compact-title-row">
                    <h2>🗓️ 每日任务</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="task-list tight-task-list" id="taskList">
                    <details class="task detailed-task" open>
                        <summary class="task-head">
                            <span class="time">08:00</span>
                            <span class="name">早晨重排</span>
                            <span class="duration">18-20分钟</span>
                        </summary>
                        <ul class="task-steps">
                            <li><strong>全身唤醒：</strong>靠墙站立 / 靠墙打开 2分钟、死虫式 10次、Bird Dog 10次</li>
                            <li><strong>坐姿修复：</strong>坐姿骨盆中立 / 前后倾找中点（8-10次，最后停20-30秒）、坐姿脚尖上勾（5秒×5次）</li>
                            <li><strong>站立走路修复：</strong>单脚站立 30秒×2、站姿提脚尖（3秒×5次）、站姿提脚跟慢放（5次）、右脚后跟找地（20-30秒）</li>
                            <li><strong>肩颈修复：</strong>W字开肩 10次、胸椎右旋 10次</li>
                        </ul>
                    </details>

                    <details class="task detailed-task">
                        <summary class="task-head">
                            <span class="time">13:00</span>
                            <span class="name">中午校正</span>
                            <span class="duration">6-8分钟</span>
                        </summary>
                        <ul class="task-steps">
                            <li><strong>全身唤醒：</strong>站姿调整右侧链 1分钟</li>
                            <li><strong>坐姿修复：</strong>坐姿骨盆中立 / 前后倾找中点（8-10次，最后停20-30秒）</li>
                            <li><strong>站立走路修复：</strong>走路时找右侧不要留在后面、前脚掌别偷偷抢支撑</li>
                            <li><strong>肩颈修复：</strong>W字开肩 10次、右后开弓动作 5-6次（每次停3-5秒）、颈部拉伸 30秒×2</li>
                        </ul>
                    </details>

                    <details class="task detailed-task">
                        <summary class="task-head">
                            <span class="time">22:10</span>
                            <span class="name">晚间重排</span>
                            <span class="duration">22-25分钟</span>
                        </summary>
                        <ul class="task-steps">
                            <li><strong>全身唤醒：</strong>靠墙站立 / 靠墙打开 2分钟、死虫式 10次</li>
                            <li><strong>坐姿修复：</strong>坐姿骨盆中立 / 前后倾找中点（8-10次，最后停20-30秒）、坐姿单腿写 A-Z、坐姿脚尖上勾（5秒×5次）</li>
                            <li><strong>站立走路修复：</strong>单脚站立 30秒×2、站姿提脚尖（3秒×5次）、站姿提脚跟慢放（5次）、右脚后跟找地（20-30秒）</li>
                            <li><strong>肩颈修复：</strong>W字开肩 10次、胸椎右旋 10次、左腰放松 2-3分钟、仰卧放松 2分钟、呼吸冥想 5分钟</li>
                        </ul>
                    </details>

                    <details class="task detailed-task">
                        <summary class="task-head">
                            <span class="time">22:45</span>
                            <span class="name">睡前记录</span>
                            <span class="duration">2分钟</span>
                        </summary>
                        <ul class="task-steps">
                            <li>整体体感：x/10</li>
                            <li>完成度：x/10</li>
                            <li>成果守住度：x/10</li>
                            <li>备注：xxx</li>
                            <li><strong>补充观察：</strong>右脚后跟有没有更敢承重、前脚掌有没有偷偷顶地</li>
                        </ul>
                    </details>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
